  "texts": [
    "In SQuADShifts Reddit, Bonito almost always extracts the answer from the paragraph, whereas GPT-4o can generate answers with additional text that may not be present in the paragraph.",
    "In ContractNLI, both models can pro-duce plausible answers.",
    "In one example, Bonito generates the question, 'Does this imply that \"This document is confidential information\"?",
    "Yes, no, or maybe?'.",
    "Bonito answers \"yes\", whereas GPT-4o produces the answer \"maybe\"."
  ],
